{"tid":521554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【統戰大揭秘】2049台灣大限？ 習帝目標兩個一百年","createTime":"2018-01-06T16:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T06:33:56.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3558110c61e7e63ef5ad43e22214c39ab813eff8","tid":521554,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180106/large/1515243730_18d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180106%2Flarge%2F1515243730_18d6.jpg&h=c4bb6875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共總書記習近平在去年10月中共十九大報告中提到，兩岸統一是中華民族偉大復興的「必然要求」，而實現這個「偉大復興」的時間是2049年，即中共建政100周年之際。換言之，中共已為統一定出「死線」，兩岸還有30年時間博弈。<br />\n<br />\n美國前駐華大使芮孝儉（Stapleton Roy）認為，習近平報告雖未明確提出統一時間表，但外界「必須把這個期限放在心上」。他認為30年時間在人類歷史不過是滄海一粟，且習曾引鄧小平的話指：台灣問題「不能留給下一代」解決，意思已經十分明確。<br />\n<br />\n習近平上台後提出兩個一百年奮鬥目標：第一個是中共成立100周年（2021年）時，內地全面建成小康社會；第二個是中共建政100周年（2049年）時，建成富強、民主、文明、和諧的社會主義現代化國家，實現中華民族的偉大復興。<br />\n<br />\n海外曾有親中媒體報道時，引北京涉台知情人士稱，習近平「肯定要在任內解決台灣問題」。習出生於1953年，到2049年將96歲，按中共現行規矩，其兩屆任期到2022年止，但有消息指當局正擬修憲改章程，為習謀求終身制鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180107/57672631\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180107%2F57672631&d=dn0RRCmRY%2FO3t512OqD4d%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=36ba5518\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180107%2F57672631&h=bb874787\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180107/57672631</a>"},{"pid":"aabbc6c59630f14fa99e75b2201785938542c098","tid":521554,"uid":48286,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:18:59.000Z","msg":"收撚皮喇支那狗<br />\n之前又話2020而家又話2040<br />\n人唔笑你自己都叫"},{"pid":"2d3c264ed676dd3564ed5b6cf9994cc31f047d04","tid":521554,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:26:52.000Z","msg":"發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33cb33ddc9e20c8c150d1b9887bd8ed9f8de693c","tid":521554,"uid":5289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:33:12.000Z","msg":"不如定聽日 啦"},{"pid":"a61da27b42a082999bdfeef4ebf5fa755fffc951","tid":521554,"uid":35790,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:50:34.000Z","msg":"咩野中華民族復興？<br />\n根本無中華民族<br />\n中華民族只係偽政治名詞"},{"pid":"42d0b7e501b5231a0b3191e397b2599deef7be4b","tid":521554,"uid":87511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3558110c61e7e63ef5ad43e22214c39ab813eff8","tid":521554,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180106/large/1515243730_18d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180106%2Flarge%2F1515243730_18d6.jpg&h=c4bb6875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共總書記習近平在去年10月中共十九大報告中提到，兩岸統一是中華民族偉大復興的「必然要求」，而實現這個「偉大復興」的時間是2049年，即中共建政100周年之際。換言之，中共已為統一定出「死線」，兩岸還有30年時間博弈。<br />\n<br />\n美國前駐華大使芮孝儉（Stapleton Roy）認為，習近平報告雖未明確提出統一時間表，但外界「必須把這個期限放在心上」。他認為30年時間在人類歷史不過是滄海一粟，且習曾引鄧小平的話指：台灣問題「不能留給下一代」解決，意思已經十分明確。<br />\n<br />\n習近平上台後提出兩個一百年奮鬥目標：第一個是中共成立100周年（2021年）時，內地全面建成小康社會；第二個是中共建政100周年（2049年）時，建成富強、民主、文明、和諧的社會主義現代化國家，實現中華民族的偉大復興。<br />\n<br />\n海外曾有親中媒體報道時，引北京涉台知情人士稱，習近平「肯定要在任內解決台灣問題」。習出生於1953年，到2049年將96歲，按中共現行規矩，其兩屆任期到2022年止，但有消息指當局正擬修憲改章程，為習謀求終身制鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180107/57672631\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180107%2F57672631&d=dn0RRCmRY%2FO3t512OqD4d%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=36ba5518\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180107%2F57672631&h=bb874787\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180107/57672631</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T17:04:21.000Z","msg":"G持雜種早日稱帝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對外宣揚大國勃起夢"},{"pid":"d591de4fcf43bf7c437c9aebe88ae1411151273e","tid":521554,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef2f27d6eae587d00a0237f8babbd07d2067df3","tid":521554,"uid":27664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:21:24.000Z","msg":"睇中國聽唔聽話啦，聽話美國就減少賣武器比台灣國，美國大把武器要賣搵錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5bb04724899559e30866e4ef15af15f3e0af198","tid":521554,"uid":97814,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T06:06:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1a77ced5670e0c9efbbe39f6415b417f9508250","tid":521554,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T06:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇中國聽唔聽話啦，聽話美國就減少賣武器比台灣國，美國大把武器要賣搵錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>賣過期垃圾順便收保護費啫 就算台灣省有F22唔通又鬥得過朝廷咩</blockquote><br />\n鬥唔過既就唔洗搵你呢d支那來炮炮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0d25618033f66f7e0ba083ebb85e0653e87911","tid":521554,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T06:24:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"305f3db76285034f0afd7041380bcdc7ebe0ff5f","tid":521554,"uid":139993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T06:33:56.000Z","msg":"我就希望佢快D打臺灣，跟住又輸比臺灣，趁早解體，正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}